      {
        "id": "docling_PPT_sociolinguistics_page_015_0",
        "observed_type": "section_header",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "Gender",
        "bbox": [
          0.39825581399691823,
          0.09302325693896804,
          0.6075581409864704,
          0.16085271195638082
        ],
        "order": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_PPT_sociolinguistics_page_015_1",
        "observed_type": "list_item",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "It has long been acknowledged that there may be differences in language usage between men and women: quite extreme in languages other than English",
        "bbox": [
          0.0566860666282927,
          0.2460317466389253,
          0.8895348728581415,
          0.45262096251592177
        ],
        "order": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_PPT_sociolinguistics_page_015_2",
        "observed_type": "list_item",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Lakoff (1975) identified extensive differences not just in grammar and lexis, but in aspects of style, register, and (especially in dialogues) dynamic roles",
        "bbox": [
          0.05668605410543776,
          0.4651162809274968,
          0.9258720859418169,
          0.620155037842475
        ],
        "order": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_PPT_sociolinguistics_page_015_3",
        "observed_type": "list_item",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Studies have adapted to the broader social agenda: early theories relating to power relationships between sexes (Lakoff) now giving way to view that there is a cultural difference (Tannen)",
        "bbox": [
          0.056686054244018354,
          0.6335978840603035,
          0.9287790732753614,
          0.8353174614091357
        ],
        "order": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_PPT_sociolinguistics_page_015_4",
        "observed_type": "list_item",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "We'll look at this issue in more detail later",
        "bbox": [
          0.05523256992286633,
          0.8468915335312497,
          0.7630813761527151,
          0.8935185176582338
        ],
        "order": 5
      }
    ]
  }
